# HIIT Timer (`projects/hiit-timer/`)

30/30 interval timer. Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS.

## Defaults

- Work: 30 seconds
- Rest: 30 seconds
- Rounds: 8 (user-configurable, saved in `localStorage`)

## Style

- Match site palette; use `--work` and `--rest` accent colors for phases
- Left-aligned layout like other projects
